*EXIT ''The Mystic Trumpeter – Live at the Roundhouse 1972, The ICES Tapes'' (pre Crass material featuring Penny Rimbaud, Gee Vaucher, John Loder and others) (Exit Stencil Music Cat No.&nbsp;EXMO2, CD and book, 2013)

